  <section name="Database documentation">
  	<subsection name="Support matrix">
    <p>
    Scarab get its database support from <a href="http://db.apache.org/torque">Torque</a>, so it should be able to run on any supported database.<br/>Anyway, given we don't have the resources to test it completely with all those systems, we need help from the community to assure it works fine.<br/>
    The following table describe the support we're able to offer *right now* to different RDBM systems, although all of them are known to have worked with Scarab from our users' experience.<br/>
    If you need help with any of them, ask for it in the mailing lists, and we will try to get it working!
